Ing '''4G''' makadaleraya ya keng pangapat a generasiun  a [[cellular wireless]] ampo ding kayang inalilan a [[3G]] ampong [[2G]] iley (standards). Ing aliwa ning articulu iti tataid ne ing '''4G''' keng ''International Mobile Telecommunications-Advanced'' (IMT Advanced), agiang ing 4G maleparan ya kabaldugan at mapaliaring kayabe la reng iley (standards) kilual ning IMT-Advanced. Ing 4G systema maliari nalang itas-antas deng kasalungsungan magagamit a communication networks ampo panaligan dalang mamie malaparan ampong makakambil a [[IP]] pagbatayan a solusiun nung nu deng facilidad antimo ing siuala, data ampong mamagus a multimedia mibie la kareng talagamit maski "kapilan" at "nokarin" man king mas mabilis a pulayi nung nu lalawen mo reng mengalabas a generasiun.


=== Paninasan ===
Ing 4G ma-alkus ya para apakiabe de ing [[:en:quality of service|QoS]] ampo ing pulayi da reng kailangan a ausan dang applications (gamit) antimo deng wireless broadband access, [[Multimedia Messaging Service]] (MMS), [[Videoconferencing|video chat]], [[mobile TV]], [[High-definition television|HDTV]] kalmanan, [[Digital Video Broadcasting]] (DVB), magnalating suyu antimo deng siuala ampong data, at aliwa pang servicio a gagamit (bandwidth).






== Gamit ==
Keng kasulungsungan a pulaying 15-30&nbsp;Mbit/s, ing 4G agiu nang mamie kareng talagamit a mamagus a [[high-definition television (HDTV)]].  Keng pulaying  100&nbsp;Mbit/s, ing kalamnan a [[DVD-5]] (antimo ing metung a palage(cine) malyari yang kuananilulan (downloaded) kilub ning 5 minutu para agamit ustung eka masuglung keng linia.



